Ranger Help for: tip arrow
===========================

SYNTAX:      goldtip arrow
             goldtip bolt
             silvertip arrow
             silvertip bolt
             tip arrow gold
             tip bolt silver
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to tip an arrow or bolt with a gold or
silver nugget, creating precious metal-tipped ammunition. The Ranger
needs ammo and a nugget, usually obtained from mining. Gold-tipped ammo
is especially accurate, while silver-tipped ammo is useful against
creatures vulnerable to silver.
